{
  "stem": "1965.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 273.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you have to thank your leader for having done this to you and the rest of your people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have nothing to do with it, but he made you a victim when he created such a genocide.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was liberated by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came to the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Russians, in her case, were her liberators.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, when we all came together in Antwerp, there used to be-- and there still is, I showed it to Tony-- a park known as [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was full of mines, full of booby traps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what they did immediately after the war, the GIs, the Americans GIs, used the German soldiers-- and the park was close to the public-- to clear away every booby trap and every mine so that the park could be reopened to the public.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know, children are teasers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as children, we would go out there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we would tease the-- I remember, I teased them too-- the Germans who were at labor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one time, one German-- this is after the war now-- lifted his shovel to hit a child.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a GI point blank killed him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's when the commander said, no more.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We cannot allow children around here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this has to be done without this kind of attendance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because you know, children have a tendency to be curious, and go, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I went in that park many, many, many times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I loved being in that park.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the thing is, no food in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You did not eat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's why when a human being goes down from 135 pounds to 68 pounds, isn't this not enough witness as to what happened, just internally to a human being, in the concentration camp?",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
